author: Reuters Editorial
title: Integer Holdings Corp Reports Q1 Non-GAAP Loss Per Share Of $0.01
text:
May 3 (Reuters) - Integer Holdings Corp:
* Q1 SALES $382 MILLION VERSUS I/B/E/S VIEW $365 MILLION * Q1 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.25
* Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.70 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* SEES 2018 GAAP SALES $1,510 MILLION TO $1,550 MILLION * SEES 2018 NON-GAAP ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER DILUTED SHARE $3.20 TO $3.50
* SEES 2018 NON-GAAP ADJUSTED SALES $1,510 MILLION TO $1,550 MILLION
* FY2018 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $3.31, REVENUE VIEW $1.51 BILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon:
